section.div: Bito CLI (Command Line Interface) provides a command line interface to the Bito AI chat functionality. Over time, CLI will add more functions and new command options to support complex automation and workflows. This is a very early Alpha version. We would love to get your feedback on the new features or improvements.
A ScrollView component that handles keyboard appearance and automatically scrolls to focused TextInput.
